chunks.html_content:
Contact the Valuation Office Agency (VOA) if you need help with things like:

  • your property’s Council Tax band
  • the rateable value of your property, if you pay business rates
  • Local Housing Allowance and fair rents

Contact your local council instead to pay your Council Tax or business rates bill.

chunks.html_content:
You can only use this service to find contact details for the VOA in England and Wales. You’ll need to contact:

  • Scottish Assessors if your property is in Scotland
  • Land and Property Services if your property is in Northern Ireland
